import React from "react";
import {NavContainer, NavItem} from './Styles/Styles'


export const TabNav = () => {

    


return(
    <NavContainer>
        <NavItem exact to={`/`}>Home</NavItem>
        <NavItem to='character-list'>Characters</NavItem>
        <NavItem to='episodes-list'>Episodes</NavItem>
        <NavItem to='locations-list'>Locations</NavItem>


        <Route exact path='/' component={WelcomePage} />

        render={(props) => <CharacterList {...props} />} />

        <Route

        render={(props) => <LocationsList {...props} />} />

    )
};
